q_en: What is the material with the highest remaining inventory?

steps.sql: SELECT m.name, wm.left_number FROM materials m JOIN warehouse_material wm ON m.id = wm.material_id ORDER BY wm.left_number DESC LIMIT 1;
steps.description: Retrieve the material name and the remaining inventory quantity for all materials in the warehouse
